    ('S759', 'NASA Thermosphere-Ionosphere-Mesosphere-Energetics-Dynamics (Timed) Satellite System', 'This assignment supports the NASA Thermosphere-Ionosphere-Mesosphere-Energetics-Dynamics (Timed) Satellite System.', 'Special'),
