    ('S763', 'Federal program using commercial contractor in non-federal space band', 'This assignment supports a Federal Government program using a commercial contractor operating in the non-federal space band. The license to operate is held by a non-federal entity in support of this program. This record is incorporated into the Government Master File for spectrum analysis, and information purposes.', 'Special'),
    ('S765', 'GLOBALSTAR Satellite System', 'This assignment supports the GLOBALSTAR Satellite System.', 'Special'),
